{"page_id": 32853, "slug": "Halo", "title": "Halo", "display_title": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Halo</span>", "namespace": 0, "content_model": "wikitext", "language": null, "wikitext": "{{expand}}\n\nA '''halo''' (天使の輪, ''tenshi no wa'') is a ring of energy that appears in association with (usually directly above) [[Angel]]s and [[Evangelion]]s in the [[Rebuild of Evangelion|Rebuild]] continuity. The only Angels that have not displayed halos so far are the [[Seventh Angel|7th]] (although the halo-like rings on its hips might qualify) and the [[Zeruel|10th]]. \n\nSome of the appearances seem arbitrary, but in general the halos accompany feats of levitation or other assisted movement, or manifest at moments when great innate power is unleashed. Gendo is seen to levitating over what appears to be a device similar to a halo in [[Evangelion 3.0]].\n\n{{MontageBox\n|float   = left\n|columns = 5\n|title   = Halo Appearances\n|colour  = \n|image1  = [[Image:Eva2-22 C0402A.jpg|thumb|[[Adams]] at [[Second Impact]].]]\n|image2  = [[Image:Rebuild1 trailer2 C27 sachi-jump 1.jpg|thumb|[[Sachiel|4th Angel]] preparing for powered jump.]]\n|image3  = [[Image:Eva1.11-Cx713.jpg|thumb|[[Shamshel|5th Angel]] rising into combat configuration.]]\n|image4  = [[File:Eva1-11 C1166 4th Angel (Ramiel).jpg|thumb|[[Ramiel|6th Angel]] approaching center of [[Tokyo-3]].]]\n|image5  = [[Image:Eva2-22 C0037 col-drop.jpg|thumb|[[Third Angel|3rd Angel]] cutting through ceiling with halo.]]\n|image6  = [[Image:Eva2-22 C0040.jpg|thumb|3rd Angel ascending via halo.]]\n|image7  = [[Image:Eva2-22 C0150 crop.jpg|thumb|center|150px|Halo-like rings on [[Seventh Angel|7th Angel]].]]\n|image8  = [[Image:Eva2-22 C0517E halo.jpg|thumb|Red halo over transformed [[Sahaquiel|8th Angel]].]]\n|image9  = [[Image:Eva2-22 C0534A2 a.jpg|thumb|Multiple halos over \"boosting\" 8th Angel.]]\n|image10 = [[Image:Eva2-22 C0980 halothar.jpg|thumb|[[Bardiel|9th Angel]] preparing for a powered jump.]]\n|image11 = [[Image:Eva2-22 C1756.jpg|thumb|[[Eva Pseudo-Evolution|Awakening]] [[Evangelion Unit-01|Eva-01]].]]\n|image12 = [[Image:Eva2-22 C1862.jpg|thumb|[[Evangelion Mark.06|Mark.06]] descending to [[Geofront]]]]\n|image13 = [[Image:Eva2-22 jikai C09.jpg|thumb|Mark.06 descending to Dogma.]]\n|image14 = [[Image:Eva2-22 jikai C12.jpg|thumb|The quickening [[Evangelion Unit-08|Eva-08]].]]\n|image15 = [[Image:Eva3-33 C0465A aaaw-halos.jpg|thumb|Concentric halos appearing under the [[AAA Wunder]] as it launches.]]\n|image16 = [[File:Eva3-33 C1348 Eva-13 Escapes.jpg|thumb|An awakened [[Eva-13]] with two Halos]]\n|image17 = [[Image:Eva3-33 C1346 09halo.jpg|thumb| Eva [[Mark.09]]/[[Vessel of the Adams]] in flight with Halo]]\n|image18 = [[File:Eva3-33 C1358 b.jpg|thumb| [[Mark.09]] landing on the Wunder; halo visible.]]\n|image19 = [[File:Eva3-33 C1358 c.jpg|thumb| [[Mark.09]] landing complete. Halo vanished.]]\n|image20 = [[Image:Eva3-33 C1293 Monoliths dead.jpg|thumb|A circle underneath a levitating Gendo.]]\n|caption = \n}}\n\n\n\n{{-}}\n\n==In ''Neon Genesis Evangelion''==\n\nThe halo motif is put to limited use in the original series. Most notably, one forms over the head of [[Evangelion Unit-00|Eva-00]] as it transitions into a giant [[Rei Ayanami|Rei]], moments before self-destructing. \n\n==In tradition==\n\nHalos are a Christian visual motif associated with angels and holy figures (such as Jesus Christ). Before they were stylized into a floating ring, they appeared in art as a circular aura from behind.{{fact}}\n\n[[Category:A to Z]]\n[[Category:Rebuild of Evangelion]]\n[[Category:Religious and Esoteric References]]\n[[Category:Terminology]]", "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table align=\"center\" style=\"border:2px solid lightseagreen; width:85%; background:honeydew;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/File:Eva2-22_C0750.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/180px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"180\" height=\"101\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/270px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/ce/Eva2-22_C0750.jpg/360px-Eva2-22_C0750.jpg 2x\" /></a></span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<p><big><b>\"<i>Making something... Nurturing something is really great. You can see and learn so many things from the process.</i>\"</b></big><br />\nPlease help improve this article or section by <b>expanding it.</b><br />\n<small>If you have questions on what to improve/expand, please discuss on the talk page.</small>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>A <b>halo</b> (天使の輪, <i>tenshi no wa</i>) is a ring of energy that appears in association with (usually directly above) <a href=\"/Angel\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Angel\">Angels</a> and <a href=\"/Evangelion\" title=\"Evangelion\">Evangelions</a> in the <a href=\"/Rebuild_of_Evangelion\" title=\"Rebuild of Evangelion\">Rebuild</a> continuity. The only Angels that have not displayed halos so far are the <a href=\"/Seventh_Angel\" title=\"Seventh Angel\">7th</a> (although the halo-like rings on its hips might qualify) and the <a href=\"/Zeruel\" title=\"Zeruel\">10th</a>. \n</p><p>Some of the appearances seem arbitrary, but in general the halos accompany feats of levitation or other assisted movement, or manifest at moments when great innate power is unleashed. Gendo is seen to levitating over what appears to be a device similar to a halo in <a href=\"/Evangelion_3.0\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Evangelion 3.0\">Evangelion 3.0</a>.\n</p>\n<table style=\"float: left; clear: left; width: 1px; text-align: center; vertical-align: center; font-size: 90%; background-color: white; border: 1px solid #aaaaaa; margin: 1em;\" cellpadding=\"2\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"background: tan; font-size: 120%; text-align: center\" colspan=\"5\"><b>Halo Appearances</b>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva2-22_C0402A.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/d/d3/Eva2-22_C0402A.jpg/300px-Eva2-22_C0402A.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d3/Eva2-22_C0402A.jpg/450px-Eva2-22_C0402A.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d3/Eva2-22_C0402A.jpg/600px-Eva2-22_C0402A.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption><a href=\"/Adams\" title=\"Adams\">Adams</a> at <a href=\"/Second_Impact\" title=\"Second Impact\">Second Impact</a>.</figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Rebuild1_trailer2_C27_sachi-jump_1.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/7/7d/Rebuild1_trailer2_C27_sachi-jump_1.jpg/300px-Rebuild1_trailer2_C27_sachi-jump_1.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"174\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7d/Rebuild1_trailer2_C27_sachi-jump_1.jpg/450px-Rebuild1_trailer2_C27_sachi-jump_1.jpg 1.5x, /images/7/7d/Rebuild1_trailer2_C27_sachi-jump_1.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption><a href=\"/Sachiel\" title=\"Sachiel\">4th Angel</a> preparing for powered jump.</figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva1.11-Cx713.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/Eva1.11-Cx713.jpg/300px-Eva1.11-Cx713.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/Eva1.11-Cx713.jpg/450px-Eva1.11-Cx713.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cc/Eva1.11-Cx713.jpg/600px-Eva1.11-Cx713.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption><a href=\"/Shamshel\" title=\"Shamshel\">5th Angel</a> rising into combat configuration.</figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva1-11_C1166_4th_Angel_(Ramiel).jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/4/4e/Eva1-11_C1166_4th_Angel_%28Ramiel%29.jpg/300px-Eva1-11_C1166_4th_Angel_%28Ramiel%29.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/4e/Eva1-11_C1166_4th_Angel_%28Ramiel%29.jpg/450px-Eva1-11_C1166_4th_Angel_%28Ramiel%29.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/4e/Eva1-11_C1166_4th_Angel_%28Ramiel%29.jpg/600px-Eva1-11_C1166_4th_Angel_%28Ramiel%29.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption><a href=\"/Ramiel\" title=\"Ramiel\">6th Angel</a> approaching center of <a href=\"/Tokyo-3\" title=\"Tokyo-3\">Tokyo-3</a>.</figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva2-22_C0037_col-drop.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/b/b8/Eva2-22_C0037_col-drop.jpg/300px-Eva2-22_C0037_col-drop.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b8/Eva2-22_C0037_col-drop.jpg/450px-Eva2-22_C0037_col-drop.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b8/Eva2-22_C0037_col-drop.jpg/600px-Eva2-22_C0037_col-drop.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption><a href=\"/Third_Angel\" title=\"Third Angel\">3rd Angel</a> cutting through ceiling with halo.</figcaption></figure>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva2-22_C0040.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/6/6b/Eva2-22_C0040.jpg/300px-Eva2-22_C0040.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6b/Eva2-22_C0040.jpg/450px-Eva2-22_C0040.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6b/Eva2-22_C0040.jpg/600px-Eva2-22_C0040.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption>3rd Angel ascending via halo.</figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-halign-center\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva2-22_C0150_crop.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/b/b3/Eva2-22_C0150_crop.jpg/150px-Eva2-22_C0150_crop.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"150\" height=\"147\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b3/Eva2-22_C0150_crop.jpg/225px-Eva2-22_C0150_crop.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b3/Eva2-22_C0150_crop.jpg/300px-Eva2-22_C0150_crop.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption>Halo-like rings on <a href=\"/Seventh_Angel\" title=\"Seventh Angel\">7th Angel</a>.</figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva2-22_C0517E_halo.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/Eva2-22_C0517E_halo.jpg/300px-Eva2-22_C0517E_halo.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/Eva2-22_C0517E_halo.jpg/450px-Eva2-22_C0517E_halo.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c9/Eva2-22_C0517E_halo.jpg/600px-Eva2-22_C0517E_halo.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption>Red halo over transformed <a href=\"/Sahaquiel\" title=\"Sahaquiel\">8th Angel</a>.</figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva2-22_C0534A2_a.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/6/61/Eva2-22_C0534A2_a.jpg/300px-Eva2-22_C0534A2_a.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/61/Eva2-22_C0534A2_a.jpg/450px-Eva2-22_C0534A2_a.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/61/Eva2-22_C0534A2_a.jpg/600px-Eva2-22_C0534A2_a.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption>Multiple halos over \"boosting\" 8th Angel.</figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva2-22_C0980_halothar.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/d/d2/Eva2-22_C0980_halothar.jpg/300px-Eva2-22_C0980_halothar.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d2/Eva2-22_C0980_halothar.jpg/450px-Eva2-22_C0980_halothar.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d2/Eva2-22_C0980_halothar.jpg/600px-Eva2-22_C0980_halothar.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption><a href=\"/Bardiel\" title=\"Bardiel\">9th Angel</a> preparing for a powered jump.</figcaption></figure>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva2-22_C1756.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/c/c8/Eva2-22_C1756.jpg/300px-Eva2-22_C1756.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c8/Eva2-22_C1756.jpg/450px-Eva2-22_C1756.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/c8/Eva2-22_C1756.jpg/600px-Eva2-22_C1756.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption><a href=\"/Eva_Pseudo-Evolution\" title=\"Eva Pseudo-Evolution\">Awakening</a> <a href=\"/Evangelion_Unit-01\" title=\"Evangelion Unit-01\">Eva-01</a>.</figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva2-22_C1862.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Eva2-22_C1862.jpg/300px-Eva2-22_C1862.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/31/Eva2-22_C1862.jpg/450px-Eva2-22_C1862.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/31/Eva2-22_C1862.jpg/600px-Eva2-22_C1862.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption><a href=\"/Evangelion_Mark.06\" title=\"Evangelion Mark.06\">Mark.06</a> descending to <a href=\"/Geofront\" title=\"Geofront\">Geofront</a></figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva2-22_jikai_C09.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Eva2-22_jikai_C09.jpg/300px-Eva2-22_jikai_C09.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fb/Eva2-22_jikai_C09.jpg/450px-Eva2-22_jikai_C09.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fb/Eva2-22_jikai_C09.jpg/600px-Eva2-22_jikai_C09.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption>Mark.06 descending to Dogma.</figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva2-22_jikai_C12.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/Eva2-22_jikai_C12.jpg/300px-Eva2-22_jikai_C12.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/Eva2-22_jikai_C12.jpg/450px-Eva2-22_jikai_C12.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2b/Eva2-22_jikai_C12.jpg/600px-Eva2-22_jikai_C12.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption>The quickening <a href=\"/Evangelion_Unit-08\" title=\"Evangelion Unit-08\">Eva-08</a>.</figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva3-33_C0465A_aaaw-halos.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/Eva3-33_C0465A_aaaw-halos.jpg/300px-Eva3-33_C0465A_aaaw-halos.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"127\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9e/Eva3-33_C0465A_aaaw-halos.jpg/450px-Eva3-33_C0465A_aaaw-halos.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9e/Eva3-33_C0465A_aaaw-halos.jpg/600px-Eva3-33_C0465A_aaaw-halos.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption>Concentric halos appearing under the <a href=\"/AAA_Wunder\" title=\"AAA Wunder\">AAA Wunder</a> as it launches.</figcaption></figure>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva3-33_C1348_Eva-13_Escapes.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/a/a7/Eva3-33_C1348_Eva-13_Escapes.jpg/300px-Eva3-33_C1348_Eva-13_Escapes.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"127\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a7/Eva3-33_C1348_Eva-13_Escapes.jpg/450px-Eva3-33_C1348_Eva-13_Escapes.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a7/Eva3-33_C1348_Eva-13_Escapes.jpg/600px-Eva3-33_C1348_Eva-13_Escapes.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption>An awakened <a href=\"/Eva-13\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Eva-13\">Eva-13</a> with two Halos</figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva3-33_C1346_09halo.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/8/81/Eva3-33_C1346_09halo.jpg/300px-Eva3-33_C1346_09halo.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"128\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/81/Eva3-33_C1346_09halo.jpg/450px-Eva3-33_C1346_09halo.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/81/Eva3-33_C1346_09halo.jpg/600px-Eva3-33_C1346_09halo.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption>Eva <a href=\"/Mark.09\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mark.09\">Mark.09</a>/<a href=\"/Vessel_of_the_Adams\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vessel of the Adams\">Vessel of the Adams</a> in flight with Halo</figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva3-33_C1358_b.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/8/8a/Eva3-33_C1358_b.jpg/300px-Eva3-33_C1358_b.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"127\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8a/Eva3-33_C1358_b.jpg/450px-Eva3-33_C1358_b.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8a/Eva3-33_C1358_b.jpg/600px-Eva3-33_C1358_b.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption><a href=\"/Mark.09\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mark.09\">Mark.09</a> landing on the Wunder; halo visible.</figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva3-33_C1358_c.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/5/52/Eva3-33_C1358_c.jpg/300px-Eva3-33_C1358_c.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"127\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/52/Eva3-33_C1358_c.jpg/450px-Eva3-33_C1358_c.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/52/Eva3-33_C1358_c.jpg/600px-Eva3-33_C1358_c.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption><a href=\"/Mark.09\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mark.09\">Mark.09</a> landing complete. Halo vanished.</figcaption></figure></td>\n<td><figure class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Thumb\"><a href=\"/File:Eva3-33_C1293_Monoliths_dead.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/images/thumb/b/bf/Eva3-33_C1293_Monoliths_dead.jpg/300px-Eva3-33_C1293_Monoliths_dead.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"128\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/bf/Eva3-33_C1293_Monoliths_dead.jpg/450px-Eva3-33_C1293_Monoliths_dead.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/bf/Eva3-33_C1293_Monoliths_dead.jpg/600px-Eva3-33_C1293_Monoliths_dead.jpg 2x\" /></a><figcaption>A circle underneath a levitating Gendo.</figcaption></figure>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align: left; valign: top;\">\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br />\n</p><p><br clear=\"all\" />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"In_Neon_Genesis_Evangelion\">In <i>Neon Genesis Evangelion</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Halo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: In Neon Genesis Evangelion\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The halo motif is put to limited use in the original series. Most notably, one forms over the head of <a href=\"/Evangelion_Unit-00\" title=\"Evangelion Unit-00\">Eva-00</a> as it transitions into a giant <a href=\"/Rei_Ayanami\" title=\"Rei Ayanami\">Rei</a>, moments before self-destructing. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"In_tradition\">In tradition</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Halo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: In tradition\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Halos are a Christian visual motif associated with angels and holy figures (such as Jesus Christ). Before they were stylized into a floating ring, they appeared in art as a circular aura from behind.<sup>&#91;<i><a href=\"/The_NGE_Fan-Geeks_Project:Standards_and_Conventions_(Eva-Specific)#Citing_Sources\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The NGE Fan-Geeks Project:Standards and Conventions (Eva-Specific)\">Source needed</a></i>&#93;</sup>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260416160747\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.039 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.045 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 204/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6916/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2157/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 5/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   11.174      1 -total\n 53.91%    6.024      1 Template:MontageBox\n 24.18%    2.702      1 Template:Expand\n 10.36%    1.158      2 Template:Br\n 10.19%    1.139      1 Template:Fact\n 10.05%    1.123      1 Template:-\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key mediawikidb-ew_:pcache:idhash:32853-0!canonical and timestamp 20260416160747 and revision id 94848. Rendering was triggered because: diff-page\n -->\n</div>", "summary": "A halo (天使の輪, tenshi no wa) is a ring of energy that appears in association with (usually directly above) Angels and Evangelions in the Rebuild continuity. The only Angels that have not displayed halos so far are the 7th (although the halo-like rings on its hips might qualify) and the 10th.", "sections": [{"toclevel": 1, "level": "2", "line": "In <i>Neon Genesis Evangelion</i>", "number": "1", "index": "1", "fromtitle": "Halo", "byteoffset": 2798, "anchor": "In_Neon_Genesis_Evangelion", "linkAnchor": "In_Neon_Genesis_Evangelion"}, {"toclevel": 1, "level": "2", "line": "In tradition", "number": "2", "index": "2", "fromtitle": "Halo", "byteoffset": 3053, "anchor": "In_tradition", "linkAnchor": "In_tradition"}], "categories": ["A to Z", "Rebuild of Evangelion", "Religious and Esoteric References", "Terminology"], "infobox": {}, "templates": ["-", "MontageBox", "expand", "fact"], "internal_links": ["Rebuild of Evangelion", "Rei Ayanami", "AAA Wunder", "Evangelion Unit-08", "Evangelion 3.0", "Ramiel", "Shamshel", "Mark.09", "Sachiel", "Seventh Angel", "Sahaquiel", "Vessel of the Adams", "Adams", "Evangelion Mark.06", "Evangelion Unit-00", "Tokyo-3", "Evangelion Unit-01", "Bardiel", "Zeruel", "Eva Pseudo-Evolution", "Second Impact", "Evangelion", "Angel", "Third Angel", "Eva-13", "Geofront"], "external_links": [], "iw_links": [], "lang_links": [], "properties": [], "protection": [], "rev_id": 94848, "length_bytes": null, "parse_warnings": [], "touched_at": null, "references": [], "chunks": [{"article_slug": "Halo", "section": "_intro", "content": "Article: Halo\nA halo (天使の輪, tenshi no wa) is a ring of energy that appears in association with (usually directly above) Angels and Evangelions in the Rebuild continuity. The only Angels that have not displayed halos so far are the 7th (although the halo-like rings on its hips might qualify) and the 10th. \n\nSome of the appearances seem arbitrary, but in general the halos accompany feats of levitation or other assisted movement, or manifest at moments when great innate power is unleashed. Gendo is seen to levitating over what appears to be a device similar to a halo in Evangelion 3.0.", "position": 0, "token_count": 139}, {"article_slug": "Halo", "section": "In <i>Neon Genesis Evangelion</i>", "content": "Article: Halo | Section: In <i>Neon Genesis Evangelion</i>\nIn Neon Genesis Evangelion\n\nThe halo motif is put to limited use in the original series. Most notably, one forms over the head of Eva-00 as it transitions into a giant Rei, moments before self-destruc", "position": 1, "token_count": 63}, {"article_slug": "Halo", "section": "In tradition", "content": "Article: Halo | Section: In tradition\nting. \n\nIn tradition\n\nHalos are a Christian visual motif associated with angels and holy figures (such as Jesus Christ). Before they were stylized into a floating ring, they appeared in art as a circular aura from behind.\n\nCategory:A to Z\nCategory:Rebuild of Evangelion\nCategory:Religious and Esoteric References\nCategory:Terminology", "position": 2, "token_count": 82}]}